                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">'police-constable K</hi> 284.) On the Sunday night I saw the prisoner and the prosecutrix—she said he took the handkerchief and money from her—he said he had not—I took him to the station—he then said he snatched the handkerchief from her, and threw it down, but be did Dot have the money—I found the handkerchief in his hat, and 5<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>., silver on him.</p>
